      "summary": "International visit to Iraq between 15 February 2026 and 20 February 2026 — Part of a delegation to Iraq to look at the state of FoRB in Kurdistan, from the perspective of churches that are registered there.  We met the Prime minister and Minister of Foreign affairs who is responsible for FoRB.  We also looked at the economy and how faiths are looked after as refugees within Kurdistan.",
